## Limitations

This report is based on the most recent data available up to October 2023. Some sources may have more recent updates that were not included. Additionally, while the report focuses on human contributions, it does not extensively cover natural factors influencing climate change. The findings are based on the selected sources and may not encompass all perspectives or emerging research in the field.